rComments: Very knowledgable and interesting lecturer! Her examples and relations to the world will definitely make you think! Not hard to do well either as long as you are clear on what is expected!
Very engaging professor and she is very passionate about her craft. Uses a lot of contemporary examples to really demonstrate an understanding to students which makes things clearer.
Emily is a very engaging professor, she really opens your eyes. If you want to learn about life, take her class.
